Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=8}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.66,Main-207+,Usopp,0,0,0,,{You almost stepped on us! - OG}You almost stepped on us, man!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.37,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,My bad, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.80,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{Wow... - OG}{My, my... - Polly}My...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:51.59,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{You got quite big... - OG}You've certainly grown...{Polly - 大きくなって means both "to grow up" and "to become big" apparently...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.30,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I'm not handing over Apple Gramps. - OG}I'm not letting you take Apple Gramps.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:57.43,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you'd just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.14,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{let me do my job. - OG}let me do my job, please.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.77,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.83,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{Whoa-whoa. - OG}Whoa, now...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.00,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:35.55,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,Go easy on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.89,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{Come on... - OG}if you wouldn't mind!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.45,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Look at him go!{OG}{Lookit him go! - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.16,Main-207+,Nami,0,0,0,,{Before it's too late, we gotta run! - OG}We gotta run before it's too late!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.62,Main-207+,Usopp,0,0,0,,{Yeah, while Luffy is holding Kizaru back! - OG}Yeah, while Luffy is keeping Kizaru busy!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.62,Main-207+,Chopper,0,0,0,,{We have to carry Robin carefully! - OG}We'll have to be careful carrying Robin!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.05,Main-207+,Chopper,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Atlas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.51,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,{I'm going down below to take back\Ncontrol of the pacifista! - OG}I'm going down there to take back\Ncontrol of the pacifista!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.18,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.22,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,as soon as the barrier goes down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.14,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,{they'll get us with their lasers! - OG}{we'll be zapped by their lasers! - Polly}they'll blast us with their lasers!{Gord+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.94,Main-207+,Edison,0,0,0,,{That's a great idea! - OG}What a capital idea!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.73,Main-207+,Edison,0,0,0,,{There's no higher authority\Nthan Vegapunk on this island! - OG}Vegapunk's the highest authority\Non this here island!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.44,Main-207+,Edison,0,0,0,,{Whoever controls the pacifista, wins! - OG}And whoever controls the pacifista wins!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.03,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,{Yeah! I'm going! - OG}Damn right! I'm off!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.74,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Wait, Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.74,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Well, but... - OG}Er, what I mean is...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.99,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,I... I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.62,Main-207+,Group,0,0,0,,– What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.21,Main-207+,Usopp,0,0,0,,{You can't possibly go! - OG}There's no way you're going!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.04,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Why?! - OG}Why not?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:51.54,Main-207+,Usopp,0,0,0,,{Because this whole thing\Nis about them trying to kill you! - OG}{All this stuff is happening\Nbecause they're trying to kill you! - Polly}This whole thing is happening\Nbecause they're trying to kill you!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.63,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{But... - OG}Yes, but...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.67,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Hey, Franky{-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.80,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Franky-kun, do you hear me?! - OG}{\i1}Franky, can you hear me?!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.63,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.80,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems like Bonney is down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.18,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{She's alive?! That's great! - OG}She's alive?! That's great news!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.06,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{She was kicked by Kizaru\Nand slammed into the barrier... - OG}Kizaru kicked her hard—right into the barrier!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.81,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Kicked?! - OG}He {\i1}kicked{\i0} her?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.23,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{How does a grown man\Nlike you let her get kicked?! - OG}{You're a grown man!\NHow could you let her get kicked?! - Polly}Aren't you a grown man?!\NHow could you let her get kicked?!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.69,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{It's my bad! I'm sorry! - OG}{I get it man, I'm sorry! - Polly}I get it, man! My bad!{Gord+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.69,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna go save her! - OG}I'll go save her right now!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.65,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.78,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But the barrier... - OG}But there's still the barrier...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.53,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{I've made up my mind. I'm going! - OG}That's it! I'm going too!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.12,Main-207+,Usopp,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.87,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Edison can deactivate the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.21,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.71,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,This is Sanji speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:39.63,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{If you're going to rescue Bonney-chan, count me in! - OG}If you're gonna rescue Bonney, count me in!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:44.35,Main-207+,Jinbe,0,0,0,,{Vegapunk. We've picked up\Nall your so-called luggage. - OG}Vegapunk. We've picked up\Nthe luggage you mentioned.{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.18,Main-207+,Jinbe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll head toward the rear exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.98,Main-207+,Jinbe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's all meet up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.65,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Run, run, run! - OG}Go, go, go!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.56,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{Oh no! - OG}Oh, crap!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.23,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Something just moved... - OG}What was that?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.94,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.69,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{Come on! It's this way! - OG}Get a move on! It's this way!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.57,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.66,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{I guess it's dangerous here, too. - OG}Guess I'm not safe here, either.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.05,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{I'm right here! - OG}Over here!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.31,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{What was that scream?! - OG}What was that?!{Polly - hmm... the OG sounds best, but it's 17 CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.27,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Answer me! - OG}Come in!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.60,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:34.94,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.48,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:39.78,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.49,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,Jewelry–
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.33,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Those at the center of town! Report! - OG}Town central team! Give me a status report!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.67,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:55.38,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{You... - OG}{You little...! - Polly}Why, you...!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.40,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:21.03,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Oh no! - OG}Report!{Nikki}{Polly - OG seems to be a mistranslation; he's saying 報告, "Report", as in giving a report}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.57,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{We've all been turned\Ninto children or old people! - OG}We've all been turned into\Nchildren and seniors!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:26.82,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Dammit!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.83,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Stay away from the town center! - OG}Stay away from the center of town!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.66,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{We believe Jewelry Bonney the pirate is there! - OG}We believe the pirate Jewelry Bonney is there!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.63,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{She's hiding somewhere! Be careful! - OG}She must be hiding somewhere! Be on guard!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.00,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,She'll manipulate your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.13,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Where'd that troublemaker scamper off to? - Polly - Not subbed by CR; Manga says ほのれどこへ消へた; I think it's probably おのれどこへ消えた but like an old man but this is a complete guess}Where'd that blasted kid get off to?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.92,Secondary-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{It's heavy! - OG}It's too heavy!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.42,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Find her! - OG}She must be nearby!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.09,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{She must be around here somewhere! - OG}Find Bonney and take her out!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.22,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.68,Secondary-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{\an8}{[/an8] - Hey! Right here! - OG}{Hey, over here! Found 'em! - Polly}Hey, over here!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.60,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{We found Sentomaru! - OG}Sentomaru has been located!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.39,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.81,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,he's burned to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.11,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,Sentomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.62,Flashbacks-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,S-Sentomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.50,Flashbacks-207+,Sentomaru,0,0,0,,Bonney...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.09,Flashbacks-207+,Sentomaru,0,0,0,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.84,Flashbacks-207+,Sentomaru,0,0,0,,The Marines are coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.10,Flashbacks-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,Sentomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.22,Thoughts-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:32.97,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Have you found her? - OG}Was she there?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:33.77,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{No! - OG}No, sir!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:34.68,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,Go check that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.56,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:40.94,Thoughts-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{I wonder if I can hide until it's all over. - OG}Can I stay hidden until this all blows over?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:48.95,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.83,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{Come out already! - OG}Get out here already!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.91,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,Let us do our job, Roronoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.12,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.10,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{Even if you hide, - OG}It doesn't matter if you hide...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.02,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{even if you move around, - OG}{It doesn't matter if you try to run... - Polly}It doesn't matter if you move around...{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.10,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I can tell where you are. - OG}I know exactly where you are...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.40,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{Because of that animal stench! - OG}because you stink like an animal!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.07,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{You're fighting! - OG}{You having a fight? - Polly}{In a fight, huh? - Z}You're really going at it!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:10.07,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Zoro, want my help? - OG}{Zoro! Need any help? - Polly}Zoro! Want a hand?{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.53,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{No, I don't! - OG}I'm just... fine!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:24.25,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Just focus on Kizaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.61,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,If this is the best you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:52.57,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{don't expect to get a chance\Nto go up against our captain. - OG}don't expect to get another shot\Nat facing our captain.{Polly+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.08,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{You're surely strong enough... - OG}Whatever you say.{Polly - there is nothing about "strength" directly in the JP so it's not necessary to keep it, although it's definitely implied. This is just a "certainly," which seems to follow up into the next line, but I guess you could also take as a response to Zoro's. It's kind of a boring line in JP anyway. Breaking it up like "You really are..." is really awkward in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.45,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{to be the number two of an Emperor. - OG}You're still an Emperor's right-hand man.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.54,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{Killing you would be rewarding. - OG}You're well worth killing on your own.{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:23.35,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,I'm going to... fall into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.77,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{I'm going to... - OG}Seems like...{Polly}
