Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.53,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Get in, Sanji-kun! Bonney! - OG}Sanji, Bonney! Get in!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:07.62,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,The pacifista are on our side now!\NLet's head back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:09.74,Main-207+,Bluegrass,0,0,0,,Shake it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:12.00,Main-207+,Bluegrass,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:07.09,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{It's no use resisting! - OG}There's no use resisting!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.80,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{You can't defeat us! - OG}You don't stand a chance!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:12.01,Thoughts-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{He never learns. - OG}This guy never learns.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:37.29,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{We have our reasons. - OG}We have our own reasons\Nfor doing this too, you know.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:42.46,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I don't care! - OG}Don't care!{Polly}{Who cares?! - Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.89,0:24:56.73,Main-207+,Lucci,0,0,0,,{You guys are toast! - OG}This is the end of the line for you guys!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.39,0:25:02.02,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{Bark all you want! - OG}{I've had enough of your barking! - Polly}You can bark all you want!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:19.21,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, but if I spend all my time on you,\NI won't be able to complete my mission! - OG}{I apologize, but if I spend all my time\Non you, I can't complete my mission. - Polly}Apologies, but if I spend all my time on you,\NI won't be able to complete my mission.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.29,0:25:25.84,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{And that's... - OG}That's the idea!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.01,0:25:29.63,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}{my mission! - OG}My{\i0} mission is to waste your time!{Polly - this is "adding information" but it sounds REALLY weird without it based on the length of VA; something like "And that's... *my* mission!" is OK I guess, but boy does it sound flat}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.03,0:25:54.37,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{What do I do? - OG}What to do...?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.41,0:25:59.00,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Wait! - OG}Hold it!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.26,0:26:13.76,Main-207+,Nami,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.26,0:26:15.64,Main-207+,Chopper,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.64,0:26:17.60,Main-207+,Chopper,0,0,0,,{I don't know what it is, but... - OG}I'm not sure what it is, but...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.60,0:26:21.06,Main-207+,Jinbe,0,0,0,,{What's this unearthly presence? - OG}{What is this unearthly presence? - Polly}What is this haunting presence?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.66,0:26:40.62,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{I can't believe this! - OG}What in the world...?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.66,0:26:44.96,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,Stand down, pacifista.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:54.97,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.97,0:26:58.01,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{The pacifista stopped guarding us! - OG}{The pacifista have stopped protecting us! - Polly}The pacifista have stopped escorting us!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.01,0:26:59.76,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,Come on, pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.76,0:27:01.72,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,{Protect us! - OG}You're supposed to keep us safe!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.72,0:27:04.14,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,{Follow my order! - OG}I gave you an order!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:06.90,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{What's happening?! - OG}What's up with this?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.98,0:27:12.32,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,{The only ones who are above us\Non the authority hierarchy... - OG}The only ones above us\Nin the authority hierarchy...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.74,0:27:13.95,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,are...{OG}{would be... - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.86,0:27:16.74,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,the Five Elders!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.12,0:27:21.29,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Is it an enemy attack?! - OG}Are we under attack?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.92,0:27:34.38,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{A pentagram?! - OG}A summoning circle?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.27,0:27:46.44,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{What the... - OG}What the hell?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.44,0:27:48.94,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{This is odd! Get to high ground! - OG}Something's off! We need\Nto get to higher ground!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.94,0:27:49.65,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Right!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.53,0:27:55.24,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{Soldiers on the island! - OG}{Attention, all Marines! - Polly}Attention, all Marines on land!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.61,0:28:00.70,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead! - OG}St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead shortly!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.20,0:28:05.41,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{No one below the rank\Nof commodore may behold him! - OG}{No one below the rank of commodore\Nis permitted to even be in his presence! - Polly}No one below the rank of commodore\Nis permitted to behold him!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.66,0:28:07.87,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,An Elder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.87,0:28:09.33,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.33,0:28:13.92,Main-207+,Doberman,0,0,0,,{\i1}{St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead! - OG}St. Saturn of the Five Elders\Nwill make landfall on Egghead shortly!{Polly - 27:55}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.72,0:28:24.14,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{What's that explosion?! - OG}What the hell is up with that explosion?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.72,0:28:28.48,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{The Five Elders?! One of them\Ncame all the way to this island?! - OG}The Five Elders?! One of them\Ncame all the way to the island?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.48,0:28:29.85,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,{The Five Elders?! - OG}"Five Elders"?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:31.52,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.52,0:28:33.57,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{They're the highest authorities in the world! - OG}Only the highest authority in the world!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:34.98,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.84,0:28:59.22,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,{Something's coming out of there! - OG}Something's coming out...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.62,0:29:26.87,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{What's that? - OG}What {\i1}is{\i0} that?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.87,0:29:28.37,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,It's a monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.37,0:29:29.29,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{Cut it out! - OG}Don't say that!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.62,0:29:31.21,Main-207+,Marine,0,0,0,,{That must be... - OG}It has to be...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.01,0:29:41.76,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{Solid ground... - OG}The surface...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.34,0:29:45.18,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,It has been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.14,0:29:52.35,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,{What's that monster?! - OG}{What the hell is that thing?! - Polly}Is that some kind of monster?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.52,0:29:55.52,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.52,0:29:56.48,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Swerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.15,0:30:02.36,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.36,0:30:04.57,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.57,0:30:06.78,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Oh no! The island clouds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.50,0:30:10.91,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Kizaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.17,0:30:17.88,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Stop right there! Kizaru! - OG}Hold it right there, Kizaru!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.42,0:30:22.80,Main-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{I think you're reaching\Nyour limit with that form... - OG}You have to be reaching\Nyour limit with that form by now...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.80,0:30:24.80,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Please, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.80,0:30:28.81,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.52,0:30:36.36,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Count on– - OG}I'm on it–{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.20,0:30:46.66,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:51.62,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.33,0:30:53.04,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,75)}Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.97,0:31:10.06,Thoughts-207+,Kizaru,0,0,0,,{This is no good! - OG}Well now... this isn't good.{Polly}{Well, this is a problem... - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:17.23,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,Nika...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.57,0:31:28.37,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I've reached my limit... - OG}Time's up...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.25,0:31:43.59,Main-207+,Franky,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.59,0:31:45.59,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{Not to worry. - OG}Not to worry, I'm alright.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.59,0:31:47.59,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Atlas{-chan}, are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.59,0:31:48.55,Main-207+,Atlas,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.60,0:31:57.31,Main-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,Are you St. Saturn?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.31,0:31:58.86,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{Indeed. - OG}Indeed I am.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.32,0:32:05.78,Main-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{I thought you were already dead, Vegapunk. - OG}I was certain we had\Nkilled you already, Vegapunk.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.12,0:32:16.58,Flashbacks-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,I gave you an order, Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.09,0:32:27.13,Main-207+,Sanji,0,0,0,,Bonney{-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.09,0:32:34.06,Flashbacks-207+,Saturn,0,0,0,,{You will not leave him any free will! - OG}You are not to leave him an ounce of free will!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.73,0:32:39.90,Flashbacks-207+,Vegapunk,0,0,0,,{But then Kuma... - OG}But if I do that, then Kuma...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.87,0:32:59.83,Main-207+,Bonney,0,0,0,,St. Saturn!
